Turkey University Guide for Students","alternateName":"Road to Study in Turkey","publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/postdoctoral-research-opportunities-in-turkey/#webpage","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/postdoctoral-research-opportunities-in-turkey/","name":"Postdoctoral Research Opportunities in Turkey - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2026-05-17T14:00:00+03:00","dateModified":"2026-05-17T14:00:00+03:00","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#website"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat","url":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","image":{"@type":"ImageObject","@id":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","url":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9f5b866231ae7aed7a61015846c1f0ab6c5797b065ec200b93c5e9daa87897af?s=96&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g","caption":"Murat","inLanguage":"en-US"}},{"@type":"BlogPosting","headline":"Postdoctoral Research Opportunities in Turkey - RoadtoStudy","datePublished":"2026-05-17T14:00:00+03:00","dateModified":"2026-05-17T14:00:00+03:00","articleSection":"Health and Safety","author":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/author/murat/","name":"Murat"},"publisher":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/#person"},"description":"Discover postdoctoral research opportunities in Turkey. Learn about available funding and support to take your career to the next level!","name":"Postdoctoral Research Opportunities in Turkey - RoadtoStudy","@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/postdoctoral-research-opportunities-in-turkey/#richSnippet","isPartOf":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/postdoctoral-research-opportunities-in-turkey/#webpage"},"inLanguage":"en-US","mainEntityOfPage":{"@id":"https://roadtostudy.com/en/postdoctoral-research-opportunities-in-turkey/#webpage"}}]}]}', "content_html" = '<h2 id="turkiyede-doktora-sonrasi-arastirma-firsatlari-neler-bekliyor" class="wp-block-heading">Postdoctoral Research Opportunities in Turkey: What to Expect?</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Turkey has been attracting attention, especially in recent years, with its investments in scientific research. Universities offering many opportunities for academics who want to conduct postdoctoral research provide the chance to participate in various projects. For example, institutions like <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/turkiye-tubitak-burslari/">TÜBİTAK</a> (The Scientific and Technological Research Council of Turkey) and YÖK (The Council of Higher Education) provide financial support for postdoctoral research projects. This support offers a great opportunity for researchers to bring their projects to life.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Example: TÜBİTAK 2232 Program</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">TÜBİTAK&#8217;s 2232 program supports Turkish researchers who want to conduct postdoctoral research abroad. This program encourages researchers to gain international experience and share this experience upon their return to Turkey.</p>
<h2>Postdoctoral Researcher Salaries and Scholarships (TÜBİTAK Examples)</h2>
<p>Projects and scholarship programs supported by The Scientific and Technological Research Council of Turkey (TÜBİTAK) offer specific figures for postdoctoral researchers:</p>
<h3>1. Salary within the Scope of TÜBİTAK Projects (1001 Program)</h3>
<p>If a postdoctoral researcher is part of a <b>TÜBİTAK 1001 project</b>, their salary will vary as follows:</p>
<ul>
<li><b>If Not Employed Elsewhere:</b> <b><span class="math-inline"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="mord">36,500</span><span class="mord mathnormal"> TL</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">month</span></span></span></span></span></b> (This is the full scholarship/support amount.)</li>
<li><b>For Those with Optional Insurance:</b> <b><span class="math-inline"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="mord">40,660</span><span class="mord mathnormal"> TL</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">month</span></span></span></span></span></b> (Insurance premiums are included in this salary.)</li>
</ul>
<h3>2. TÜBİTAK Domestic Postdoctoral Research Scholarship (2218 Program)</h3>
<p>This is a scholarship program that researchers who have completed their doctorates can apply for, independent of specific projects:</p>
<ul>
<li><b>Full Scholarship:</b> <b><span class="math-inline"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="mord">36,500</span><span class="mord mathnormal"> TL</span></span></span></span></span></b></li>
<li><b>Partial Scholarship:</b> <b><span class="math-inline"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="mord">10,000</span><span class="mord mathnormal"> TL</span></span></span></span></span></b></li>
<li>Additionally, researchers who qualify for this scholarship are provided with up to <b><span class="math-inline"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="mord">175,000</span><span class="mord mathnormal"> TL</span></span></span></span></span></b> in research support and a <b><span class="math-inline"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="mord">5,000</span><span class="mord mathnormal"> TL</span><span class="mord">/</span><span class="mord mathnormal">report</span></span></span></span></span></b> consultancy fee.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="turkiyedeki-universitelerin-arastirma-olanaklari-ve-destek-programlari" class="wp-block-heading">Research Facilities and Support Programs at Turkish Universities</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Many universities in Turkey offer various support programs and research facilities for postdoctoral researchers. These facilities include research infrastructure, laboratory access, and financial support.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Research Infrastructure</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Major universities, in particular, are equipped with modern research laboratories and equipment. For example, Orta Doğu Teknik Üniversitesi (ODTÜ) and <a href="https://roadtostudy.com/istanbul-teknik-universitesi/">İstanbul Teknik Üniversitesi</a> (İTÜ) have strong research infrastructures in the fields of engineering and science.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Support Programs</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Support programs offered by universities include research scholarships, project funds, and international collaborations. For example, Boğaziçi Üniversitesi offers various funds that encourage researchers to participate in international projects.</p>
<h2 id="doktora-sonrasi-arastirma-icin-basvurulmasi-gereken-kurumlar-ve-programlar" class="wp-block-heading">Institutions to Apply to for Postdoctoral Research</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">There are several important institutions and programs that those wishing to conduct postdoctoral research should apply to. These institutions provide financial support and resources to researchers.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Key Institutions</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>TÜBİTAK</strong>: Turkey’s most important scientific research institution. It provides support for postdoctoral research projects.</li>
<li><strong>YÖK</strong>: The Council of Higher Education offers various programs to increase the research capacity of universities.</li>
<li><strong>Universities</strong>: Each university has its own research funds and support programs.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="turkiyede-arastirma-yapmanin-avantajlari-ve-zorluklari" class="wp-block-heading">Advantages and Challenges of Conducting Research in Turkey</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">While Turkey offers many advantages for those wishing to conduct postdoctoral research, it also presents some challenges.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Advantages</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Developing Research Infrastructure</strong>: The modern laboratories and research centers at universities in Turkey offer extensive facilities for researchers.</li>
<li><strong>International Collaborations</strong>: Turkey participates in many international research projects, giving researchers the opportunity to build a global network.</li>
<li><strong>Affordable Cost of Living</strong>: The cost of living in Turkey is more affordable compared to many Western countries, providing an economic advantage for researchers.</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Challenges</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Language Barrier</strong>: Many academic programs in Turkey are offered in Turkish. This can be a barrier for international researchers who do not speak the language.</li>
<li><strong>Resource Limitations</strong>: In some research fields, the limited availability of necessary resources can make it difficult for research to progress.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="uluslararasi-ogrenciler-icin-turkiyede-doktora-sonrasi-kariyer-olanaklari" class="wp-block-heading">Postdoctoral Career Opportunities in Turkey for International Students</h2>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">International students can have various career opportunities in Turkey after completing their postdoctoral research.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Career Opportunities</h3>
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li><strong>Academic Career</strong>: Faculty positions at Turkish universities can be an attractive option for postdoctoral researchers.</li>
<li><strong>Research Institutions</strong>: Working at research institutions like TÜBİTAK can provide international experience.</li>
<li><strong>Private Sector</strong>: Private sector companies operating in the fields of technology and engineering are opening their doors to postdoctoral researchers.</li>
</ul>
