<h3>What program is used to make a poster?</h3>
<p>The most commonly used programs for poster creation are <b>PowerPoint</b> (for its ease of use and accessibility) and <b>Adobe Illustrator</b> (for professional graphics and print quality).</p>
<h3>What is a scientific poster?</h3>
