<p>When saving the prepared poster (in programs like PowerPoint, Illustrator, etc.), it is sufficient to select <b>PDF</b> as the output file type using the <b>&#8220;Save As&#8221;</b> option or the <b>&#8220;Export&#8221;</b> function. This preserves the print quality.</p>
