<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What kind of services do career counselors offer?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Career counselors offer guidance on resume preparation, interview techniques, and finding internships and jobs.</p>
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What steps should I follow to get career counseling in Turkey?</h3>
<p class="wp-block-paragraph">First, you can apply to your university&#8217;s career center or contact private consulting firms to receive services.</p>', '$.wp_published_at', '2026-05-15T07:00:00Z', '$.wp_modified_at', '2026-03-16T19:52:11Z') WHERE "collection" = 'posts' AND "id" = ( SELECT "live_revision_id" FROM "ec_posts" WHERE "deleted_at" IS NULL AND "status" = 'published' AND "locale" = 'en' AND "slug" = 'shape-your-future-with-career-counseling-in-turkey' );
